      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AVOID THE NOISE (2) broke a string of placings finishing in the money three on end before a last start fourth (20.23) at Capalaba. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Better than last start and worth following up. SCOTCH BON BONS (1) has missed the frame at her last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when third (19.29) at this track in a Grade 6. Well placed here and can atone this time. NEVER GIVING UP (6) was strongly fancied last time but ran below expectations when fifth (19.99), beaten 4.5 lengths. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Must be included in calculations. TARCISIA (4) picked up a cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
